peaks-to-us-personally-uniquely-and-in-ways-we-will-understand\">The Savior Speaks to Us Personally, Uniquely, and in Ways We Will Understand<\/a>,\u201d <cite>Inspiration<\/cite> (blog), JuneÂ 15, 2022, ChurchofJesusChrist.org.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"19.\" id=\"note19\" data-full-marker=\"19.\">\n<p data-aid=\"162706515\" id=\"p_f5G1Y\">See <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2?lang=eng&amp;id=p16#p16\">1Â Nephi 2:16<\/a>; notice how Nephi\u2019s heart was softened after crying unto God.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"20.\" id=\"note20\" data-full-marker=\"20.\">\n<p data-aid=\"162706521\" id=\"p_pdcoo\">See <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/19?lang=eng&amp;id=p11-p12#p11\">1Â Kings 19:11\u201312<\/a>\u2014felt the still small voice within reaching out to my mind and heart; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2?lang=eng&amp;id=p16#p16\">1Â Nephi 2:16<\/a>\u2014how God softened Nephi\u2019s heart as he prayed; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/enos/1?lang=eng&amp;id=p3#p3\">Enos 1:3<\/a>\u2014the joy of the Saints (the gospel) sunk deep into my heart; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/10?lang=eng&amp;id=p4#p4\">Moroni 10:4<\/a>\u2014pray with real intent.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"21.\" id=\"note21\" data-full-marker=\"21.\">\n<p data-aid=\"162706527\" id=\"p_qsIA4\">RussellÂ M. Nelson, \u201c<a class=\"cross-ref\" href=\"/study/broadcasts/worldwide-devotional-for-young-adults/2022/05/12nelson?lang=eng\">Choices For Eternity<\/a>\u201d (worldwide devotional for young adults, MayÂ 15, 2022), Gospel Library.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"22.\" id=\"note22\" data-full-marker=\"22.\">\n<p data-aid=\"162706533\" id=\"p_wNxls\">See <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31?lang=eng&amp;id=p13-p14#p13\">2Â Nephi 31:13\u201314<\/a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/18?lang=en